agentTypes.name: bank
dialog: 👨‍💼 While you’re here, we can exchange 🥉🥈🥇precious medals…
👨‍💼 Visit the main branch of 🏦 Bank of Dysia on the far side of the 🎲 world. 🔚

agentTypes.name: forge
dialog: 👩‍🏭 This is a forge where we do honest forgery…
👩‍🏭	Place a medal in the forge to craft a useful component…
👨‍🏭	Components can be combined to make other components…
🔩 / 🔩 🔜 🔪 You can forge knives from bolts…
🔗 / 🔩 🔜 🔨 A link over a bolt makes a hammer…

agentTypes.name: castle
dialog: 👸 Behold, stranger. I am Princess Die of Euia.
👸 The power of mojick—the transmutation of emoji—has faded from the land…
👸 With it, all the mojical creatures have vanished…
👸 The 🦄 unicorn has not been seen since The Fall…
👸 The 🐉 dragon is but a myth. 🔚

agentTypes.name: pearTree
dialog: 🌳 I am the Tree of Knotty and Nice…

agentTypes.name: captain
dialog: 💂‍♂️ Hark! I’m the Captain of the Guard…
💂‍♂️ In the forest to the 👈 west, there is a 🌳 tree that is quite unlike the others…
💂‍♂️ Soldiers use its 🍐fruit to improve their 💛 stamina when they travel in the ⛰ Eural Mountains. 🔚

agentTypes.name: major
dialog: 💂‍♀️ Hark! I’m A♯ Major in service to her Majesty 👸 Princess Die…
💂‍♀️ A friend of mine⛏ has gone missing in the ⛰ Eural Mountains, to the 👇 south…
💂‍♀️ Please help them if you can! 🔚

agentTypes.name: harriet
dialog: 💇‍♀️ Did you know that you can shear 🐑 sheep with ✂️ scissors?
💇‍♀️ That’s why scissors are an improvement over just 🔪 two knives…
💇‍♀️ I knit with 🧶 yarn and 🥢 needles…
💇‍♀️ My friend, 🧓 Jack 🔪 whittled my needles from 🪵 wood. 🔚

agentTypes.name: miner
dialog: 👨‍🔧 I came here with my sturdy ⛏ pick axe but I was trapped by this 🪨 boulder…

agentTypes.name: boulder
dialog: 🪨 But, for reasons that escape me…

agentTypes.name: jack
dialog: 🧓 A 🪵 Lumber Jack needs an 🪓 axe…
🧓 For an 🪓 axe, 🏭 forge a 🔪 knife on a 🔨 hammer. 🔚

agentTypes.name: glub
dialog: 🐟 Fish can swim over the edge of the world…
🐟 I have seen you people make them with 🥄 shovels. 🔚

agentTypes.name: owl
dialog: 🦉  Hoo many licks would it take to get to the center?…

agentTypes.name: northPole
dialog: 🎅 We were once the powerful Moji of the north…
🎅 We were the stewards of the 💨 Essence of Wind…
🤶	We seek a student to pass on our knowledge…
🎅 They must recreate the ☔️ wand of wind and water…

agentTypes.name: bee
dialog: 🐝 Long ago, I was called a dumbledore…

agentTypes.name: cow
dialog: 🐄 Then, like a 🍽 dish, you can run away with a 🥄 spoon…
🐄 Or hollow out a 🪵 log to make a 🛶 canoe…

agentTypes.name: sponge
dialog: 🧽  I’m planted, but not a plant…
🧽  I’m inanimate, yet am an animal…

agentTypes.name: southPole
dialog: 🧙‍♀️ We just live here, but don’t tell the 🐧 penguins…

agentTypes.name: recyclingPlant
dialog: 🍄 We live in the dark and eat 💩 waste…

agentTypes.name: jack2
dialog: 🧓 It’s hard to stay warm in the ❄️ frigid north…
🧓 That’s why I knit myself a 🧥 Jacket…
🧓 To knit, you’ll need 🧶 yarn and 🥢 needles…
🧓 I 🔪 whittled my needles out of 🪵 wood. 🔚

agentTypes.name: bull
dialog: 🐂 Then, like a 🍽 dish, you can run away with a 🥄 spoon…
🐂 Or hollow out a 🪵 log to make a 🛶 canoe…

agentTypes.name: brownBear
dialog: 🐻 I have fallen on hard times…

agentTypes.name: polarBear
dialog: 🐻‍❄️ I am so happy to be a polar bear again…
🐻‍❄️ Only a pair of 🕶 night shades would make me cooler…
🐻‍❄️ Thank you again for restoring my 🥼 cloak.🔚

agentTypes.name: fishingBoat
dialog: 🛥 To make one, attach a 🪝 hook…
🛥 To a 🦯 stick of some kind.🔚

agentTypes.name: pirate
dialog: 🏴‍☠️ For ye a pirate to be…
🏴‍☠️ And a handy 🪝 hook you’ll need…
🏴‍☠️ And high seas shall be y’r pleasure.🔚

agentTypes.name: blowFish
dialog: 🐡 If my size does not dissuade you…
🐡 And my spikes do fail to argue…

agentTypes.name: mountainCyclist
dialog: 🚵 They are a great store for 🥇value🥇.🔚

agentTypes.name: merman
dialog: 🧜‍♂️ Thank you for restoring my 🔱 trident…
🧜‍♂️ Imbuing them with the mojick of 💦 water…
🧜‍♂️ So you can come to me if you don’t have your own 🔱 trident.🔚

agentTypes.name: herman
dialog: 🏊‍♂️ It is a wand of 💦 water mojicks…
🏊‍♂️ Legend is that you can 🥇 gild a 🌼 lily…
🏊‍♂️ But that’s not important right now…
🏊‍♂️ Maybe you can gild a three-lobed ☘️ clover…
🏊‍♂️ You would probably need a 🏭 forge.🔚
